{"content": "I need to multiply 324 \u00d7 523 in base 9.\n\n**Step 1: Convert to base 10**\n\n324\u2089 = 3\u00d79\u00b2 + 2\u00d79\u00b9 + 4\u00d79\u2070 = 3\u00d781 + 2\u00d79 + 4\u00d71 = 243 + 18 + 4 = 265\u2081\u2080\n\n523\u2089 = 5\u00d79\u00b2 + 2\u00d79\u00b9 + 3\u00d79\u2070 = 5\u00d781 + 2\u00d79 + 3\u00d71 = 405 + 18 + 3 = 426\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Multiply in base 10**\n\n265 \u00d7 426 = 265 \u00d7 (400 + 26)\n= 265 \u00d7 400 + 265 \u00d7 26\n= 106,000 + 6,890\n= 112,890\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Convert result to base 9**\n\n112,890 \u00f7 9 = 12,543 r 3\n12,543 \u00f7 9 = 1,393 r 6\n1,393 \u00f7 9 = 154 r 7\n154 \u00f7 9 = 17 r 1\n17 \u00f7 9 = 1 r 8\n1 \u00f7 9 = 0 r 1\n\nReading from bottom to top: **181763\u2089**\n\n**Step 4: Verification**\n\n181763\u2089 = 1\u00d759049 + 8\u00d76561 + 1\u00d7729 + 7\u00d781 + 6\u00d79 + 3\u00d71\n= 59049 + 52488 + 729 + 567 + 54 + 3\n= 112,890\u2081\u2080 \u2713\n\n181763", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 1245, "completion_tokens": 464}